# huuman Design System

Mobile-first, dark-only health app running in Capacitor (iOS). CSS transitions for all interactions. No framer-motion in components. One stable dark theme (no circadian phases).

## Design Tokens (globals.css)

### Surfaces (iOS dark mode aligned, elevation = lighter)
- `bg-surface-base` (#111114) -- page background
- `bg-surface-raised` (#1C1C1E) -- cards, inputs, list items
- `bg-surface-overlay` (#2C2C2E) -- sheets, drawers, popovers
- `bg-surface-elevated` (#3A3A3C) -- active states, tooltips

### Borders
- `border-border-subtle` (#1F1F23) -- faint separators
- `border-border-default` (#2C2C30) -- standard borders (cards, inputs)
- `border-border-strong` (#3A3A3E) -- emphasized borders

### Text hierarchy
- `text-text-primary` (#fafafa) -- headings, important text
- `text-text-secondary` (#a1a1aa) -- body text, descriptions
- `text-text-tertiary` (#71717a) -- labels, captions
- `text-text-muted` (#52525b) -- timestamps, disabled, placeholders

### Domain accent colors (3 intensities each)
Import `domainStyle` from `@/lib/domain-colors` for all domain-specific styling. Never define local domain color maps.

- Cardio: `text-domain-cardio`, `bg-domain-cardio-muted`, `text-domain-cardio-bright`
- Strength: `text-domain-strength`, `bg-domain-strength-muted`, `text-domain-strength-bright`
- Mindfulness: `text-domain-mindfulness`, `bg-domain-mindfulness-muted`, `text-domain-mindfulness-bright`
- Nutrition: `text-domain-nutrition`, `bg-domain-nutrition-muted`, `text-domain-nutrition-bright`
- Sleep: `text-domain-sleep`, `bg-domain-sleep-muted`, `text-domain-sleep-bright`

### Semantic colors
- `text-semantic-success` / `bg-semantic-success` / `bg-semantic-success-muted` -- completions, positive
- `text-semantic-warning` / `bg-semantic-warning` / `bg-semantic-warning-muted` -- caution, attention
- `text-semantic-error` / `bg-semantic-error` / `bg-semantic-error-muted` -- errors, destructive
- `text-semantic-info` / `bg-semantic-info` -- informational

### Overlay
- `bg-[--color-overlay]` -- scrim for sheets and dialogs

### Radii
- `rounded-radius-sm` (8px), `rounded-radius-md` (12px), `rounded-radius-lg` (16px), `rounded-radius-xl` (20px)

## Typography
Font: Inter (loaded via `next/font/google` in layout.tsx). Sizes match iOS Dynamic Type.

| Class | Size | iOS Style |
|---|---|---|
| `text-xs` | 11px | Caption 2 |
| `text-sm` | 13px | Footnote |
| `text-base` | 15px | Subheadline |
| `text-lg` | 17px | Body / Headline |
| `text-xl` | 20px | Title 3 |
| `text-2xl` | 24px | Title 2 |

Weights: `font-normal` (400), `font-medium` (500), `font-semibold` (600).

## Interactions (CSS only)

All press feedback uses CSS transitions. No framer-motion `whileTap` or `motion.button`.

### Press feedback
- Buttons: `active:scale-[0.97] active:brightness-110 transition-[transform,filter] duration-100`
- Cards: `active:scale-[0.99] transition-transform duration-100`
- Icon buttons: `active:brightness-125 transition-[color,filter] duration-100`
- Text buttons: `active:opacity-70 transition-opacity`

### Expand/collapse
Use CSS grid for height animation: `grid grid-rows-[0fr]` -> `grid-rows-[1fr]` with `transition-[grid-template-rows] duration-200` on the container, `overflow-hidden` on the inner div.

### Enter/exit
Use CSS keyframes `fadeIn` and `scaleIn` (defined in globals.css). Apply via `animate-[fadeIn_150ms_ease-out]`.

## Haptics (lib/haptics.ts)

Import from `@/lib/haptics`. Call on meaningful interactions.

- `haptics.light()` -- selections, toggles, navigation taps
- `haptics.medium()` -- form submissions, sheet open, primary actions
- `haptics.heavy()` -- destructive actions
- `haptics.success()` -- session completed, plan generated

## Components (components/ui/)

Always use these instead of raw HTML elements:

| Component | Import | Purpose |
|---|---|---|
| `<Button>` | `@/components/ui/Button` | All tappable buttons (primary, secondary, ghost, danger) |
| `<IconButton>` | `@/components/ui/IconButton` | Icon-only buttons with 44px hit area |
| `<Input>` | `@/components/ui/Input` | Text inputs with min-h-[44px] and focus ring |
| `<Toggle>` | `@/components/ui/Toggle` | iOS-exact toggle (31x51px) via Radix Switch |
| `<Badge>` | `@/components/ui/Badge` | Domain and semantic badges |
| `<Skeleton>` | `@/components/ui/Skeleton` | Loading placeholders |
| `<Card>` | `@/components/ui/Card` | Card with Header/Body/Footer |
| `<Sheet>` | `@/components/ui/Sheet` | Bottom sheet via Vaul with Header/Body/Footer |
| `<NavHeader>` | `@/components/ui/NavHeader` | Navigation bar for sub-pages with back button |
| `<ConfirmDialog>` | `@/components/ui/ConfirmDialog` | iOS-style confirmation dialog (replaces confirm()) |
| `<ScrollToBottom>` | `@/components/ui/ScrollToBottom` | FAB for chat scroll |
| `<Avatar>` | `@/components/ui/Avatar` | Avatar with onError fallback |

Toast: call `toast()` / `toast.success()` / `toast.error()` from `sonner`.

## Navigation Pattern

The app uses header-icon navigation (no TabBar):

- **Chat header**: Avatar (left, opens ProfileSheet) + "huuman" (center) + Data icon (right, navigates to /data)
- **Data pages**: NavHeader with back chevron to return to chat
- **Overlays**: Sheet for settings/profile, ConfirmDialog for destructive confirmations
- **Never use** `confirm()`, `alert()`, or `window.location.reload()`

## Touch targets

All standalone tappable elements must be at least **44px** in both dimensions (Apple HIG). `Button` and `IconButton` enforce this via `min-h-[44px]`.

## Domain color utility

Import `domainStyle` from `@/lib/domain-colors` for domain-specific UI:
```
import { domainStyle } from "@/lib/domain-colors";
const style = domainStyle[session.domain]; // .text, .bg, .bright, .border
```

## Anti-patterns (NEVER do these)

1. **Never use raw zinc values** -- use semantic tokens (`bg-surface-raised` not `bg-zinc-900/50`)
2. **Never import framer-motion** -- use CSS `active:` + `transition` for press feedback
3. **Never use `hover:` without `active:`** -- mobile has no hover. Use `active:` only.
4. **Never use spinners for loading** -- use `<Skeleton>` components
5. **Never use `confirm()` or `alert()`** -- use `<ConfirmDialog>`
6. **Never use `window.location.reload()`** -- use `router.refresh()`
7. **Never define local domain color maps** -- import `domainStyle` from `@/lib/domain-colors`
8. **Never create touch targets below 44px** -- use `Button`/`IconButton` which enforce minimums
9. **Never hardcode spacing** -- use the 4px grid via Tailwind spacing utilities
10. **Never forget safe-area padding** -- bottom bars need `safe-bottom` class
